01:03:15.320 --> 01:03:20.080
that you need to figure out what happened and get back on track.


01:03:20.080 --> 01:03:23.720
And so Blackbox is a backup system.


01:03:23.720 --> 01:03:27.360
It's designed to be extremely easy to work with,


01:03:27.360 --> 01:03:29.240
like abstract away all the painful stuff.


01:03:29.240 --> 01:03:32.280
And it's also designed to be really easy to contribute to.


01:03:32.280 --> 01:03:34.840
I've been working on trying to make


01:03:34.840 --> 01:03:38.160
