01:03:38.160 --> 01:03:39.640
Big fat read me.


01:03:39.640 --> 01:03:41.320
Everything's like abstract classes.


01:03:41.320 --> 01:03:43.240
So if you want to contribute, you usually only


01:03:43.240 --> 01:03:47.960
