01:04:16.320 --> 01:04:18.960
Then you tell it, where do you want to store that backup?


01:04:18.960 --> 01:04:20.640
Maybe you want to store it in an S3.


01:04:20.640 --> 01:04:23.200
Maybe you want to store it on Dropbox or something free


01:04:23.200 --> 01:04:24.120
